<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Quiz Non Disponible - DevQuiz Pro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header-content">
          <div class="quiz-info-section">
            <div id="quizTitle" class="quiz-title">Quiz Non Disponible</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="quiz-main-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="quiz-content-wrapper">
          <div class="no-data-container">
            <div class="no-data-card">
              <div class="no-data-icon">
                <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="64" height="64">
                  <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15h2v2h-2v-2zm0-8h2v6h-2V9z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 class="no-data-title">Quiz Non Disponible</h2>
              <p class="no-data-message">
                Désolé, le quiz "<%= quizType %>" n'a pas encore de questions disponibles.
                <br>
                Veuillez réessayer plus tard ou choisir un autre quiz.
              </p>
              <div class="no-data-actions">
                <a href="/quiz/list" class="btn btn-primary">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M19 12H5"/>
                    <polyline points="12,19 5,12 12,5"/>
                  </svg>
                  Retour aux Quiz
                </a>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
                    <polyline points="9,22 9,12 15,12 15,22"/>
                  </svg>
                  Tableau de Bord
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <style>
      .no-data-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 60vh;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .no-data-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .no-data-icon {
        color: #f59e0b;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .no-data-title {
        color: #1f2937;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .no-data-message {
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .no-data-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        min-width: 160px;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .btn svg {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background-color: #3b82f6;
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #2563eb;
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background-color: #6b7280;
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.3);
      }

      .btn-secondary:hover {
  
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.4);
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .no-data-card {
          padding: 2rem;
          margin: 1rem;
        }

        .no-data-actions {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 1rem;
        }

        .btn {
          width: 100%;
          min-width: auto;
        }
      }
    </style>

  </body>
</html>
